| Metric | Current | Target | Gap |
|--------|---------|--------|-----|
| **Statements** | 41.7% | 80% | +38.3pp |
| **Lines** | 43.4% | 80% | +36.6pp |

### Current Test Infrastructure
- **108 test files** / **177 test suites** / **1,737 tests** — all passing
- Coverage excludes: test files, .d.ts, index.ts barrels, __mocks__

### Key Untested Areas (Highest Impact)

| Priority | Area | Impact | Why |
|----------|------|--------|-----|
| 🔴 P0 | `context/AuthContext.tsx` | ~300 LOC | Auth logic — critical path |
