### Effort Estimate to Reach 80%

Going from **43% → 80%** requires covering ~3,000 additional lines across ~60 untested files. This is approximately **15-20 new test files** with **300-400 new test cases**.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Reaching 80% coverage from 43% is a multi-session effort. The current 108 test files / 1,737 tests form a solid foundation. Focus on P0 items (auth, store, sync) first for maximum safety impact.

